 <body>
  <p>A <strong><i>Content Manager</i></strong> for AEM Screens is a creative professional who works closely with marketing and knows the campaign, audience, and the desired focus. The content manager is responsible for creating and orchestrating end-user experience by developing different channels and assigning sequences into a timed channel experience.</p> 
  <p>Content Manager for Screens design locations and schedules, maintain channel integrtity, perform analytics and reporting, and maintain video profiles.</p> 
  <p>An AEM Screens content manager is responsible for the following tasks:</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li>Design Locations</li> 
   <li>Design Schedules</li> 
   <li>Maintain Channel Integrity</li> 
   <li>Video Profiles</li> 
  </ul> 
